================================================================================
                                     Groot                                      
================================================================================

`Groot`:t: uses genomic data to produce an `N-Rooted Fusion Graph`_::


    \         /       /
     A       B       C       ⬅ Roots
      \     /       /
       \   /       /
        \ /       /
         AB      /           ⬅ Fusion product
          \     /
           \   /
            \ /
            ABC              ⬅ Fusion product
              \

.. note::

    Full documentation can be found here_.

`Groot`:t: is licensed under the GNU AGPLv3_.

